quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  12,5,"Qala ya bunayya la taqsusru/yaka AAala ikhwatika fayakeedoo laka kaydan innaashshaytana lil-insani AAaduwwun mubeen"
  12,6,"Wakathalika yajtabeeka rabbukawayuAAallimuka min ta/weeli al-ahadeethi wayutimmuniAAmatahu AAalayka waAAala ali yaAAqooba kamaatammaha AAala abawayka min qablu ibraheemawa-ishaqa inna rabbaka AAaleemun hakeem"
  12,7,"Laqad kana fee yoosufa wa-ikhwatihi ayatunlissa-ileen"
  12,8,"Ith qaloo layoosufu waakhoohu ahabbuila abeena minna wanahnu AAusbatuninna abana lafee dalalin mubeen"
  12,9,"Oqtuloo yoosufa awi itrahoohuardan yakhlu lakum wajhu abeekum watakoonoo min baAAdihiqawman saliheen"
  12,10,"Qala qa-ilun minhum lataqtuloo yoosufa waalqoohu fee ghayabati aljubbi yaltaqithubaAAdu assayyarati in kuntum faAAileen"
  12,11,"Qaloo ya abana malaka la ta/manna AAala yoosufa wa-innalahu lanasihoon"
  12,12,"Arsilhu maAAana ghadan yartaAAwayalAAab wa-inna lahu lahafithoon"
  12,13,"Qala innee layahzununee an thathhaboobihi waakhafu an ya/kulahu aththi/buwaantum AAanhu ghafiloon"
  12,14,"Qaloo la-in akalahu aththi/buwanahnu AAusbatun inna ithan lakhasiroon"
